OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMuch of the low cloud should
OL,6,Fclear during the morning, but it could
OL,7,Fbe rather persistent through northern
OL,8,FAberdeenshire. Light or moderate north
OL,9,For northwest winds. Feeling a bit
OL,10,Fcooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome evening sunshine away
OL,13,Ffrom the far north, then the cloud
OL,14,Fthere will extend south across much of
OL,15,Fthe region tonight, with the odd light
OL,16,Fshower.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FA cloudy start for most, the
OL,19,Fodd light shower, then all areas will
OL,20,Fbrighten up with some good sunny
OL,21,Fspells in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
