OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells on Sunday, then cloudier in
OL,7,Fevening, patchy rain. Cloudy Monday,
OL,8,Fpatchy rain, then drier, brighter
OL,9,Flater. Tuesday dry, some sunny
OL,10,Fintervals, turning warmer.
